====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[come]] [[near]] to; to be [[close]] to; to come into [[contact]]
#: {{zh-x|接觸|to touch; to come into contact}}
# to [[receive]]
#: {{zh-x|接受|to accept; to receive}}
#: {{zh-x|交接|to transfer; to hand over}}
# to [[host]]; to receive or [[admit]] someone
#: {{zh-x|接待|to host (visitors)}}
# to [[catch]]
#: {{zh-x|接球|to catch a ball}}
# to [[continue]]; to [[follow]]
#: {{zh-x|接續|to continue; to relay}}
#: {{zh-x|接二連三|to follow one another}}
#: {{zh-x|再接再厲|to keep on}}
# to [[take over]]
#: {{zh-x|接管|to take over}}
# to [[connect]]
#: {{zh-x|接口|(computing) interface}}
#: {{zh-x|嫁接|to graft}}
# to [[pick up the phone]]
#: {{zh-x|無人 接聽|nobody's answering}}
# to [[meet]], [[greet]] and [[welcome]] {{gl|someone}}; to [[pick up]] {{gl|a person}}
#: {{zh-x|我 而家 揸 緊 車 去 機場 接 你。|I'm driving to the airport to '''pick''' you '''up''' right now.|C}}
# {{surname|zh|xlit=Jie}}

